.TH "i40e_aq_rx_ctl_read_register" 9 "i40e_aq_rx_ctl_read_register" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
i40e_aq_rx_ctl_read_register \- use FW to read from an Rx control register
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "i40e_status" i40e_aq_rx_ctl_read_register
.BI "(struct i40e_hw *hw "  ","
.BI "u32 reg_addr "  ","
.BI "u32 *reg_val "  ","
.BI "struct i40e_asq_cmd_details *cmd_details "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hw" 12
pointer to the hw struct
.IP "reg_addr" 12
register address
.IP "reg_val" 12
ptr to register value
.IP "cmd_details" 12
pointer to command details structure or NULL
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Use the firmware to read the Rx control register,
especially useful if the Rx unit is under heavy pressure
